T02TD3701E:335a-0: @335a * // nor rgyun ma'i mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad bzhugs//
T02TD3701E:335a-2: # // 'phags ma nor rgyun ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3701E:335a-3: gzugs bzang gzugs mdzes mchog ster ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-4: nor 'dzin byed ma nor rgyun ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-5: nor dpal dpal mdzad mchog gyur ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-7: skyabs gyur gus la mnyes gshin pa //
T02TD3701E:335a-8: lha mo shes rab pha rol phyin //
T02TD3701E:335a-9: shes rab dpal dang blo 'phel ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-10: rig 'dzin zhi ba phra mo ste //
T02TD3701E:335a-12: sgrol ma sgrol 'jug lha mo ste //
T02TD3701E:335a-13: rigs sbyin dbang phyug dbang phyug ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-14: rgyan ma 'byung po'i yum gyur ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-15: rgyan rnams kun gyis brgyan byed ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-16: gdul dka' sgrub mdzad 'jigs byed ma //
T02TD3701E:335a-17: drag mo drag po mchog tu gnon //
T02TD3701E:335a-18: lha mo sbyin pa'i pha rol phyin //
T02TD3701E:335b-0: char 'bebs @335b bzang po'i gzugs can ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-1: gter dang bkra shis thams cad dang //
T02TD3701E:335b-2: grags dang dpal dang snyan mdzad dge //
T02TD3701E:335b-3: sreg ma gsod ma gtum mo ste //
T02TD3701E:335b-4: 'tshe byed ma mo thams cad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-5: gshin rje skrag mdzad drag nyid ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-6: gzhon nu ma dang sna tshogs gzugs//
T02TD3701E:335b-7: lha mo brtson 'grus pha rol phyin //
T02TD3701E:335b-8: 'gro ba dga' mdzad can ma ste //
T02TD3701E:335b-9: dka' thub ma dang drag gzugs ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-10: rdzu 'phrul grub pa mchog ster ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-11: skal bzang bsod nams skal ba che //
T02TD3701E:335b-12: mi thub thub pa pha rol gnon //
T02TD3701E:335b-13: 'gro la gcig tu phan brtson ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-14: g-yul las sgrol byed dge ba mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-15: lha mo bzod pa'i pha rol phyin //
T02TD3701E:335b-16: tshul khrims bsam gtan sgom mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-18: padma'i gdan la bzhugs pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-19: dag pa'i gzugs can gzi brjid che //
T02TD3701E:335b-20: gser gyi mdog can 'od mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-21: yid bzhin nor bu 'dzin lha mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-22: shes rab glegs bam 'dzin pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-23: gter gyi phung por bzhugs mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-24: nor dang ldan mdzad nor dga' ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-25: khams gsum dbang phyug chen mo ste //
T02TD3701E:335b-26: lha yi rgyan gyis brgyan pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-27: sangs rgyas kun gyi yum gyur ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-28: rin chen khams kyi dbang phyug ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-29: dngos po stong nyid bsgom lha mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-30: dngos dang dngos med rnam spang mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-31: gdul bar bya ba 'dul mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-32: sgrol ma nyon mongs spyod pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-33: bdud rnams thams cad 'joms pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-34: sa 'og bdun po skyong mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-35: bram ze ma da dmigs byed yum //
T02TD3701E:335b-36: sbas ma phug tu gnas pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-37: dbyangs can ma dang spyan yangs ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-38: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi ldan pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-39: de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes chen ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-40: rdo rje can ma rdo rje 'chang //
T02TD3701E:335b-42: sna tshogs dbang phyug sna tshogs 'bar //
T02TD3701E:335b-43: sprin gyi dkyil 'khor ldan pa mo //
T02TD3701E:335b-44: sems can kun gyis rtogs mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-45: byang chub yang dag thob mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-46: bsam gtan mos pa phun tshogs ma //
T02TD3701E:335b-47: gnyis med gnyis med sgom mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-2: bud med gzugs can dkar mo gnon //
T02TD3701E:336a-3: sangs rgyas las rnams ston mdzad ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-4: ngag gi dbang mo ston ma che //
T02TD3701E:336a-5: srung mdzad 'dzin mdzod nor ster ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-6: bud med gzugs 'dzin grub pa mo //
T02TD3701E:336a-8: yid 'phrog ma dang gzugs mdzes ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-9: skal bzang dga' ba ston pa mo //
T02TD3701E:336a-10: ded dpon ma dang brtse ldan ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-11: de bzhin gshegs kun bdag nyid ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-12: nor rgyun lha mo khyod la 'dud //
T02TD3701E:336a-13: sems can kun gyi don ster ma //
T02TD3701E:336a-14: bzang po'i gzugs can khyod la 'dud //
T02TD3701E:336a-15: nor rgyun ma khyod la phyag 'tshal //
T02TD3701E:336a-16: mtshan ni brgyad lhag brgya pa ni //
T02TD3701E:336a-17: gang zhig dus gsum klog byed pa //
T02TD3701E:336a-18: yid kyi shing rtas 'dod byed pa //
T02TD3701E:336a-19: thams cad nges par thob par 'gyur //
T02TD3701E:336a-20: mtshams med pa dang cha mthun gang //
T02TD3701E:336a-21: shin tu mi bzad las rnams ni //
T02TD3701E:336a-22: de rnams thams cad mtshan bzang po //
T02TD3701E:336a-23: rjes su dran las zad par 'gyur //
T02TD3701E:336a-24: yang na tshul khrims phun sum tshogs //
T02TD3701E:336a-25: skye ba bdun ni dran pa dang //
T02TD3701E:336a-26: dga' dang tshig btsun gzugs bzang ldan //
T02TD3701E:336a-27: mthong dga' bram ze rgyal rigs kyi //
T02TD3701E:336a-28: rigs ni phyug por skye bar 'gyur //
T02TD3701E:336a-29: mthar ni sa yi dbang thob nas //
T02TD3701E:336a-31: ming brgya rtsa brgyad bklags pa yis //
T02TD3701E:336a-33: 'phags ma nor rgyun ma'i mtshan brgya rtsa brgyad pa rdzogs so//
